by KamilKubicki at 2021-04-23T06:53:28Z

Just tested the feature for:
- ordinary messages (text & title fields)
- MessageCards (Title, Text, ThemeColor, ActionCard, Facts & Sections, Inputs)

feature seems to be working as expected:

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/13560497/115830107-21e4b200-a410-11eb-9c0c-21b376a0f7f5.png)
```php
    $input = new TextInput();
    $input->id('input_title');
    $input->isMultiline(true)->maxLength(5)->title('Input Title');
    $inputDate = new DateInput();
    $inputDate->title('Input Date Title')->id('input_date');
    $microsoftTeamsOptions = (new MicrosoftTeamsOptions(
        [
            '@type' => 'MessageCard',
            '@context' => 'https://schema.org/extensions',
        ]
    ))
        ->title('Title')
        ->summary('Summary')
        ->themeColor('#0076D7')
        ->section(
            (new Section())
            ->title('Section - name')
            ->fact((new Fact())
                ->name('Section Fact 1')
                ->value('Section Fact 1 value')
            )
            ->fact((new Fact())
                ->name('Section Fact 2')
                ->value('Section Fact 2 ')
            )
        )
        ->action((new ActionCard())
            ->name('ActionCard - name')
            ->input($input)
            ->input($inputDate)
            ->action((new HttpPostAction())
                ->name('Add comment')
                ->target('http://target')
            )
        );

```
I will prepare appropriate documentation for the feature and complete missing parts (if any).

